<div class="post-content">

<h2>Build Your Own Nightmares</h2>
<p>The core concept behind Tyke and Sons Lumber Co. is brilliantly simple: everything you build during the day becomes your enemy at night. As Mike — grandson of the legendary (and mysteriously vanished) Chipper — you spend your days planting trees, gathering resources, and constructing increasingly sophisticated robots called Chipo-Mats to automate your lumber business. But once the sun goes down, those same machines wake up and come hunting.</p>

<p>This "two games in one" approach is what sets it apart from every other FNAF fan game. Neither half feels like an afterthought. The daytime sections are a fully-realized crafting adventure with boss fights, minigames, underwater exploration, and an expanding map. The nighttime horror is a tense, FNAF 4-inspired survival experience with its own unique mechanics and progression system. As one reviewer put it: <em>"unlike Pizza Sim, I think this game does the whole two-games-in-one thing way better."</em></p>

</div>

